instance variables - within class, but outside of methods!
	 //help us descripbe class
	 

    method header : eg. public static void main(<args>) // all modifiers,args, and name    

    method signature: just method NAME and parameters // main(args)

    
instantiable classes: classes that we reuse/ invoke

variables inside methods have no modifiers (public / private) !!!!


